flowchart TD
    client([Web client])

    subgraph backend [Backend]
        auth[User authentication]
        api[Key directory API]
        submitter[CometBFT API client]
    end

    subgraph cmt [CometBFT testnet]
        rpc[CometBFT RPC]
        consensus[Consensus engine]
        abci[ABCI app]
        state[(Replicated state<br/>key directory)]
    end

    client -->|HTTPS| auth
    auth --> api
    api --> submitter
    submitter -->|broadcast_tx_sync| rpc
    rpc --> consensus
    consensus -->|DeliverTx, Commit| abci
    abci --> state
    client -.tx_search.-> rpc